    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345140/extras/2a40bddb384f52ea1153621e351d7349.poster.avif?t=1693941054\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345140/extras/2a40bddb384f52ea1153621e351d7349.webm?t=1693941054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345140/extras/2a40bddb384f52ea1153621e351d7349.mp4?t=1693941054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Day In Day Out is a fascinating game that allows you to immerse yourself in the world of Mr. Lüneberg. The varied collection of mini-games, inspired by events of daily life, offers a unique gaming experience. <br><br>In the game, you have the opportunity to take on different characters and objects in Mr. Lüneberg's daily life. Whether you're playing as a fly in a waiting room, a photocopier in the office, or a popcorn-hungry boy in the horror movie theater, you'll experience a wide range of situations. <br><br>In addition to the captivating storyline, Day In Day Out also offers a challenge in the form of highscore lists. Play against others and try to become the best everyday player! <br><br>Experience the beauty and challenges of daily life in a completely new way with Day In Day Out. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tAn emotional journey of the everyday<br></li><li>\tEight different mini-games<br></li><li>\tHighscores!<br></li><li>\tShort mini-games for in-between<br></li><li>\tMusic by Louis Nostitz</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345140/extras/a225bd947a35760d9c81426482c0f0a8.poster.avif?t=1693941054\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass